    <item>
      <title>市政债券破产暂停创纪录 暂时提振市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/record-hiatus-of-muni-bankruptcies-cheers-market-for-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国各州和各市的资产负债表强劲，市政破产对免税债券投资者来说已成为遥远的记忆。一些策略师警告称，联邦援助的终止可能会加剧信贷担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/record-hiatus-of-muni-bankruptcies-cheers-market-for-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 17:33:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
