    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利的威尔逊认为股市几乎没有熊市迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-sees-few-signs-of-bear-market-in-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利的迈克·威尔逊表示，尽管季节性因素不佳和增长前景不明朗可能会限制美国股市在本季度剩余时间内的涨幅，但股市全面崩溃的可能性很小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-sees-few-signs-of-bear-market-in-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 17:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛和摩根大通称市场预期经济衰退的可能性上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/goldman-jpmorgan-say-markets-pricing-in-higher-recession-odds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，市场动荡一度引发华尔街恐慌，此后金融市场发出警告称，经济衰退即将来临的可能性更高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/goldman-jpmorgan-say-markets-pricing-in-higher-recession-odds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 16:57:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安大略省教师基金会回报率达 4.2%，任命前 Brookfield 执行首席财务官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/ontario-teachers-posts-4-2-return-names-ex-brookfield-executive-cfo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安大略省教师退休金计划今年上半年实现了 4.2% 的回报，这得益于股票和大宗商品（尤其是黄金）投资的推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/ontario-teachers-posts-4-2-return-names-ex-brookfield-executive-cfo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉吉收入下降，因交易员难以实现利润目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/cargill-s-revenue-declines-almost-10-from-record-levels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉吉公司 (Cargill Inc.) 最近一个财年的收入下降了近 10%，这一下滑源于这家全球最大农作物贸易商出现盈利困境的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/cargill-s-revenue-declines-almost-10-from-record-levels</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 12:19:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
